Available immediately. Pets Negotiable. No Animal Deposit. Animal Fee of $30 per month. Well maintained house with hardwood floors, carpeting, and ceramic tile. Kitchen is in great condition with stainless appliances, including refrigerator, microwave, oven and dishwasher. Ample space to entertain in backyard with mature trees and deck. Located in Stone Oak area--residence is close to highways, shopping, restaurants, and in a great school district. 
300 off first full month's rent if leased by 01/01/18**  Rent Includes: Condo/HOA Fees
